text:
Oh... it looks great.
It suits you well.

Hehe, thank you!
I really like it too.

...Look, here.
There are feathers attached, see?

It somehow feels very "283", I thought.
Like having wings, you know...
I'm looking forward to standing on stage...!
Haha... I'm looking forward to it too.

As a producer, and...
...as one of your fans.

...Yes!
Please watch closely from the front row.

With this costume,
I'll soar high!
